thread.title: Valued Customer

author: Valued Customer
title: Valued Customer
text: I'll have to admit, even after reading the reviews, I was still skeptical of the service. I went ahead and made the purchase to unlock my device. About 36 hours later, I got an email saying my device had been unlocked so I checked and sure enough it had been! I'll tell you, it's not an immediate process, so just be patient. You can always check the status online as well. Overall, I am very pleased with my purchase and the service I was given.
